{"tid":2039362,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"許智峯，峯峯，各位點評價佢？","createTime":"2020-05-28T03:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T06:15:24.000Z","uid":213877,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1b803547ff3d7f6b0c1b444636a72058b76e7959","tid":2039362,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T03:42:47.000Z","msg":"許智峯，峯峯，各位點評價佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5be7e228b6a9a03fa72421579c9a0cae7653ce","tid":2039362,"uid":213877,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T03:43:34.000Z","msg":"二讀辯論3度暫停 許智峯擲腐爛植物議員掩鼻逃<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200528/_2020052811125766047.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200528%2F_2020052811125766047.jpg&h=fb8347ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會今日續會繼續二讀辯論《國歌法》。民主派朱凱廸、陳志全、許智峯分別被逐離場，會議3度暫停。其中，許智峯在議事廳內投擲惡臭腐爛植物，不少議員在會議暫停期間掩鼻離場。議事廳及後緊急疏散，立法會秘書處報警，消防到場處理，警方在場搜證。<br />\n<br />\n會議早上開始約8分鐘後，民主派議會陣線朱凱廸因展示「最佳主席李慧琼」標語，被立法會主席梁君彥逐離場，朱凱廸認為裁決不公拒絕離開，梁君彥暫停會議，朱凱廸由保安抬走。<br />\n<br />\n早上約10時15分會議恢復，梁君彥解釋朱凱廸所展示的「最佳主席李慧琼」標語「反諷」具侮辱性，所以逐他離場。期間，人民力量陳志全不滿裁決，離座指罵梁君彥並拒絕返回座位，被梁君彥驅逐，泛民議員則阻止保安抬走陳志全，梁君彥第2度暫停會議。<br />\n<br />\n早上約10時47分會議恢復後，許智峯衝出座位，向主席台前擲出一袋傳出惡臭的腐爛植物，梁君彥逐許智峯離場並第3度暫停會議，保安及清潔人員清理現場，以布蓋著腐爛植物，並在議事廳四周噴曬清毒噴霧及空氣清新劑等。<br />\n<br />\n由於腐爛植物氣味難聞，不少議員掩鼻離場。議事廳及後緊急疏散，立法會秘書處報警處理，消防員於早上約11時過後到場處理，警方拍照紀錄及搜證。許智峯事後解釋，擲出的物品是前兩日已腐爛的盆栽，而透過腐爛植物抗議是意味本港的制度及法治已腐爛，讓建制派議員感受一下腐爛的味道。"},{"pid":"0931408db308789c7b30e8b2d820fe8d7536985e","tid":2039362,"uid":22288,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T03:45:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d0f94a3509f5d26877170f1dc5b03623ee47cf1","tid":2039362,"uid":134415,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T03:47:17.000Z","msg":"Good job<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ac6dfd5ce3f8493559668530540996598b5ddf","tid":2039362,"uid":247032,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T03:47:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持"},{"pid":"2dee5b90ed86844d15301f8d9c9b4ffbc0babc0b","tid":2039362,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T03:48:44.000Z","msg":"新招數！"},{"pid":"fc29b281c465a415c103aaa7838dd6a8ac229ae2","tid":2039362,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T03:48:57.000Z","msg":"臭男人許智峯"},{"pid":"fec6716325065826ec409ddadd4d5dd4e0c266ee","tid":2039362,"uid":185066,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T03:49:44.000Z","msg":"佢做左要做既本分 唔洗過份讚揚 總好過手足企係出面打生打死阻開會"},{"pid":"ee208b85fab9d9ea18386e375a4031573b0355ae","tid":2039362,"uid":17263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T03:51:44.000Z","msg":"有味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c6a033e03f9e04cf7c4df8c893eae4e60431b4","tid":2039362,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T03:52:16.000Z","msg":"有聽民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有實際行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f147d1e894a5785c170139225f5f157d1b4021f","tid":2039362,"uid":279835,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T03:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"debbc5d7f04d7b849fa328827aa4d80d694f1579","tid":2039362,"uid":229369,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T03:55:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔小心<br />\n論論盡盡</span><br />\n<br />\n靚靚花盆都攞唔實<br />\n點畀佢做我哋伙計？<br />\n睇佢咁嘅撚樣攞碌警棍都冇辦法亂咁揮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4b4ef94c211d836913f9501cacd86854baa5bf","tid":2039362,"uid":287051,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T03:55:26.000Z","msg":"咁大頭蝦打瀉晒搞到一地都係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a47d6d66a4470661dcebef877702f4f67b4595","tid":2039362,"uid":276676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T04:04:24.000Z","msg":"根本有勇武魂<br />\n泛民得佢最似我哋要嘅議員"},{"pid":"f2bc0ba8780a6b27516b8838f8dd40668fdf317f","tid":2039362,"uid":154106,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T05:27:20.000Z","msg":"佢好似出選港島，佢己經攞左我個票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071b16d45ca58e1eb93d82f91eb7852d97067c92","tid":2039362,"uid":311171,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T05:31:29.000Z","msg":"許智勇"},{"pid":"872efb0d10ee758547ab9a88adaf02d322ba4369","tid":2039362,"uid":283040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T06:15:24.000Z","msg":"自上年六月，佢係泛民之中上得最多前線，依家更被黑警針對的立法會議員。<br />\nsalute <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}